&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why InterWorks&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;InterWorks is a people-focused tech consultancy that empowers clients with customized, collaborative solutions, and we love pursuing innovation alongside people who inspire us. Our approach to work and community is unique and unconventional—just like us—and that’s the way we want it. The only thing missing is you.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;At InterWorks, we value unique contributions, our people are the glue that holds our business together.&amp;nbsp; We’re always looking for the right people, and we could be your perfect fit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Senior Data Consultant&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Melbourne, Victoria, Australia&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Can you turn a messy business problem into a data strategy that actually moves the needle? Do you want to be in the room where decisions get made, shaping the conversation, framing the trade-offs and connecting technical possibility to real business value? At InterWorks, we’re looking for a Senior Data Consultant who leads with outcomes, earns trust quickly and backs it up with deep technical credibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a senior, client-facing role for someone who has done the hands-on data work and wants the strategic, value-focused side of consulting. You’ll own the most important client relationships, shape solutions before a line of code is written and guide organizations from “we have a data problem” to “here’s the business case, here’s the roadmap, here’s the value we’ll unlock.” Success in this role shows up in business conversations, trusted advisory and the technical outcomes you help clients achieve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is based in our Perth, Australia office. Remote work or telecommuting outside this location isn’t available for this position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Salary range commensurate with experience and qualifications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead business value conversations with senior stakeholders, uncovering the real problem, framing opportunities in commercial terms and connecting data initiatives to measurable outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the data solution design process from start to finish, translating ambiguous business needs into clear, pragmatic architectures and roadmaps clients can act on with confidence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a trusted advisor and the senior point of contact across your engagements, building long-term relationships that grow accounts and earn repeat work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide clients through complex data challenges, balancing strategy, governance and delivery realities to recommend the right solution, not just the most technical one.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide architectural direction across the full stack: cloud data platforms (Snowflake, Databricks and similar), the cloud infrastructure that supports them (compute, storage, networking, security and cost) and the AI capabilities layered on top.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and advise on AI and GenAI solutions, from RAG and LLM-powered applications to ML pipelines, and help clients separate genuine value from hype while planning for governance, security and responsible use.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design cloud infrastructure architectures that are scalable, secure and cost-optimised, and translate infrastructure trade-offs into terms business stakeholders can act on.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and elevate consultants and engineers, raising the bar on how the team connects technical work to business impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Roll up your sleeves to deliver work alongside our team of AI, IT, data, analytics and strategy experts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You’ll Need&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Must-Haves&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience across data architecture, data consulting or solution delivery, including significant time in senior client-facing or advisory roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proven record of leading business value conversations and translating commercial objectives into data strategies and solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to design solutions and architectures that solve business problems, not just technical ones, and to explain the trade-offs clearly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication, facilitation and stakeholder management skills, able to hold the room with executives and technical teams alike.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A solid technical foundation: high proficiency in SQL, strong data modelling skills and a working command of modern cloud data platform architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
